# Work in Progress – Link Station

**MANDATORY:** Before starting any Link Station coding task, read the **"Current work in progress"** section in `CONTEXT.md`. Use it as the primary task list.

- Add items when the user asks you to do something. Complete them step by step. Check them off `[ ]` → `[x]` in CONTEXT.md when done.
- When all items are complete, **delete the content** of "Current work in progress" (section header stays). Leave a placeholder like *Empty – add tasks when starting new work.*
- Do not ignore or forget remaining work when taking on new tasks.
